OL,3,CVictim of hit-and-run named as man
OL,4,Ccharged with murder
OL,6,FThe family of a hit-and-run victim
OL,7,Fhave described their "indescribable
OL,8,Fpain" after a man appeared in court
OL,9,Fcharged with his murder.
OL,11,FNajib Maghsodi, 26, was walking on
OL,12,FPrince's Street, Doncaster, when he
OL,13,Fwas hit by a car on Friday at 8.32pm.
OL,14,FHe died in hospital.
OL,16,FA silver Hyundai car which was
OL,17,Finvolved in the collision failed to
OL,18,Fstop at the scene.
