OL,3,CVictim of hit-and-run named as man
OL,4,Ccharged with murder
OL,6,FStefan Wheeler, 31, appeared at
OL,7,FDoncaster Crown Court on Monday
OL,8,Fcharged with murder and driving
OL,9,Foffences. He was remanded in custody
OL,10,Fto appear at the same court on Tuesday.
OL,12,FIn a statement, Mr Maghsodi's family
OL,13,Fsaid: "Najib was taken from us far too
OL,14,Fsoon. He was the most amazing, kind,
OL,15,Fand beautiful husband, son, and soon
OL,16,Fto be dad.
OL,18,F"We are beyond words and the pain is
OL,19,Findescribable."
